snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP LOST ALMOST ALL HIS MONEY TO AMBER
snippet.description:
Hey Guys! Welcome back to a brand new video from our channel.

Johnny Depp Reveals How Much Money Amber Stole From Him 
Amber Heard and Johnny Depp have been duking it in court for years now. And this legal battle has cost them several thousand dollars if not millions. But between them both, Johnny Depp has lost way more money due to this legal battle that has been going on for years.
So, how much money has Johnny Depp lost and how did he lose it?
